{"tid":1461111,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[記者朋友速入] 跪求一陣可唔可以幫手問警犬汽油彈做假單嘢？","createTime":"2019-08-13T06:17:07.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-13T06:28:24.000Z","uid":73381,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"48579a2d5591c421d6db5c95c36bf75fbef6e9bf","tid":1461111,"uid":73381,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T06:17:07.000Z","msg":"一開始問清楚受傷隻狗係邊個位受傷 佢哋唔可能無紀錄<br />\n<br />\n如果佢答係大南西街 即刻問佢點解要做假新聞 因為嗰到嘅汽油彈係完全無燒到警犬<br />\n<br />\n仲有之前北角單嘢一樣係講大話 問佢警隊係唔係可以公然向市民做假？<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n開多次係時事台 技術性屌打央視汽油彈假新聞<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1460548\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1460548</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n警察知法犯法做假新聞？<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1460057\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1460057</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"8e45bc6fe7b8d2bebe5d486c929960f3a64b38d7","tid":1461111,"uid":73381,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T06:17:37.000Z","msg":"定係佢哋口中嘅汽油彈其實係路由器？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"461cfdf03d18f45345dd6515a41c8bc284442155","tid":1461111,"uid":73381,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T06:18:05.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9d6785ab919455df10e7f70d5df516cec2267064","tid":1461111,"uid":41584,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T06:18:14.000Z","msg":"對付林鄭，要草船借箭<br />\n催淚彈已經係常餐，會唔會有手足去禮賓府開餐<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1451531\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1451531</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"0b778473a508bd1760576a602ce1e78143b9905b","tid":1461111,"uid":73381,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T06:19:29.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" c