>\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: green;\"><div style=\"text-align: center;\"> 林鄭將香港推向一個萬劫不復的深淵<br />\n林鄭月娥忍心將香港推進粉身碎骨深淵<br />\n五大訴求 缺一不可</div></span></span><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: blue;\"><div style=\"text-align: center;\"> 黑警假扮示威者掟磚同火魔法<br />\n記者請日日問</div></span></span>"},{"pid":"d2f93af8db73cf76b3c000651e84bfb3a0bada00","tid":1461111,"uid":301479,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T06:24:26.000Z","msg":"<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\"> 香港警方=黑社會=恐怖主義組織</span></span></div><br />\n811--黑 警假扮示威者掟磚同火魔法<br />\n811--尖沙咀 6名警察扮示威者 帶隊召黑衫人 帶頭燒警署<br />\n811--銅鑼灣 警察扮示威者射丫叉 混入人群搞事後表露身分制服旁人同時大量防暴增援<br />\n811--以化學武器攻擊葵芳/太古車站內<br />\n811--北角警察無視白衣人攻擊黑衣人及記者<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: green;\"><div style=\"text-align: center;\"> 林鄭將香港推向一個萬劫不復的深淵<br />\n林鄭月娥忍心將香港推進粉身碎骨深淵<br />\n五大訴求 缺一不可</div></span></span><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: blue;\"><div style=\"text-align: center;\"> 黑警假扮示威者掟磚同火魔法<br />\n記者請日日問</div></span></span>"},{"pid":"7cae670b62253ad3adfe0f4a1582170ce50cafcf","tid":1461111,"uid":301479,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T06:24:42.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: blue;\"><div style=\"text-align: center;\">林鄭將香港推向一個萬劫不復的深淵<br />\n林鄭月娥忍心將香港推進粉身碎骨深淵<br />\n記者請日日問<br />\n</div></span></span>"},{"pid":"426d1ac619cf86d60798d41fee5c7059ef4ffdaf","tid":1461111,"uid":301479,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T06:24:56.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: blue;\"><div style=\"text-align: center;\">林鄭將香港推向一個萬劫不復的深淵<br />\n林鄭月娥忍心將香港推進粉身碎骨深淵<br />\n記者請日日問<br />\n</div></span></span>"},{"pid":"07756e42a30f051733bc74e7c3ceb0264c89fcdc","tid":1461111,"uid":301479,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":